title: Woody's
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Organic, Take-out
description: Organic vegetarian restaurant. Pleasant space with pine tables and views of the canal. Live music some evenings. Directions: By train, Apsley BT station is just across the road. By car Apsley is on the A4251 either from the magic roundabout in Hemel town centre or on the A4251 from M25, junc. 20.
